@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gpfire(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.37)) + wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.97)))
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.31)) + (0.64 + (v0 + 0.62 * tmp + 0.90)))
    v0 = ((0.25 * 0.92) * (0.70 - 0.45))
    v2 = (v2 * 0.46)
    data[tid] = v0
